show.description: Caught between duty and desire, Ira finds herself bound to a devil she swore to destroy. But what happens when the lines between enemy and savior blur? "Shaitaan ki Baahon Mein" is a twisted tale of rebellion, secrets, and forbidden fire. Watch Now.
